      <body>
         <div type="edition" xml:lang="la" xml:space="preserve">
            <!-- The content of this "div" element is not (as of 2012-11-03-04:00) conformant
                 EpiDoc. It is simply text that has been copied, leiden siglan and all, into this
                 document from the initial spreadsheet. It will need to be converted into proper
                 EpiDoc encoding.-->
               <ab>
                  <lb n="1"/>Tuqu<surplus>a</surplus>e, o sanctis
                  <lb n="2" break="no"/>sima coniunx, felix
                  <lb n="3"/> morte tua neque in
                  <lb n="4"/> hunc servata dolore<supplied reason="undefined" evidence="parallel">m</supplied>!
                  <lb n="5"/> ne crudelis fili fac <g type="hedera"/>
                  <lb n="6" break="no"/>ta videres <g type="hedera"/> <space quantity="2" unit="character"/>
                  <lb n="7"/> et vos felices dulcissi
                  <lb n="8" break="no"/>mae filiae relicto fra
                  <lb n="9" break="no"/>tre indigno nomine
                  <lb n="10"/> <space quantity="3" unit="character"/> vestro <space quantity="4" unit="character"/>
               </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>And you, o most sacred wife,
               <lb n="2"/>fortunate in your death, not reserved for this grief,
               <lb n="3"/>may you not see the deeds of [your] cruel son, 
               <lb n="4"/>and you, fortunate sweetest daughters, with a brother left behind, 
               <lb n="5"/>unworthy of your name.
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <listApp>
               <app>
                  <note>The final words could read "in digno nomine," rendering a translation "in your worthy name."</note>
                  <note>The first four lines of this inscription quote <name ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/8194433/#Virgil">Vergil</name>, Aeneid 11.158-9.</note>
               </app>
            </listApp>
         </div>
      </body>
